These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  electrician, entrepreneur, mechanic, paramedic, photographer, social-worker, videographer
7 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, dog, goldfish, bird, rabbit, ferret
 1. the paramedic is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
 2. the owner of the bird is the paramedic##1
 3. the videographer is on the right of the social-worker##1
 4. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 5. the mechanic is in the middle##1
 6. the owner of the cat is on the far left##1
 7. the photographer is the owner of the cat##1
 8. the electrician is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 9. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
10. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the mechanic##1
11. the videographer is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Job           | photographer | paramedic | entrepreneur | mechanic | electrician | social-worker | videographer |
| Pet   | cat    | bird   | goldfish      | rabbit | dog    | chinchilla    | ferret         |

