.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
There 7 different types of food: cranberry, cucumber, eggplant, nectarine, peach, raspberry, watermelon
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: february, september, april, july, october, january, march
 1. the person who's birthday is in october is the person eating nectarine##1
 2. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 5. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 6. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in october is in the middle##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person eating peach##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
10. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Food          | cranberry | cucumber | peach | nectarine | raspberry | watermelon | eggplant |
| Birthday   | september      | april   | july   | october      | february       | march       | january     |

