.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
There 7 different types of food: corn, cucumber, lemon, lettuce, onion, pepper, spinach
The people have 7 different hobbies: board-games, baking, cooking, card-games, collecting, drawing, woodworking
 1. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating onion##1
 2. the person eating onion is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 3. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
 4. the person eating corn is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
 5. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person eating onion##1
 6. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 7. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 8. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 9. the person eating pepper is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
10. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
11. the person who's hobby is card-games is in the middle##1
12. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Food   | cucumber | onion     | lemon  | pepper       | corn       | spinach  | lettuce   |
| Hobby    | drawing  | board-games | woodworking | card-games | baking | cooking | collecting |

