.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
City: marseilles, venice, london, hamburg, miami, new-york, paris
There are 7 different nationalities: argentine, australian, egyptian, indian, indonesian, nigerian, thai
 1. the person traveling to miami is the australian##1
 2. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
 3. the nigerian is on the right of the egyptian##1
 4. the argentine is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
 5. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 6. the person traveling to new-york is on the far left##1
 7. the egyptian is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
 8. the person traveling to london is on the right of the nigerian##1
 9. the person traveling to london is the indonesian##1
10. the indonesian is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
11. the thai is the person traveling to venice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| City   | new-york    | paris     | hamburg     | london      | venice | miami      | marseilles     |
| Nationality   | indian | egyptian | nigerian | indonesian | thai | australian | argentine |

