The people's birthday is in 7 different months: march, december, august, january, may, october, july
 1. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person who's birthday is in july##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is in the middle##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 8. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 9. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
10. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Hobby   | cooking | drawing | sudoku     | gardening | video-games | magic-tricks | board-games |
| Birthday     | july   | august    | may | october     | march         | january     | december        |

